    <form action="/qSubmit">
          <h3>FAQ</h3>

          <label id="question">How do I sign up for a lesson? </label>
          <label id="answer">Go to "Looking to Learn" from the home screen and pick an activity that you want to learn! </label>

          <label id="question">How do I pay for a lesson? </label>
          <label id="answer">Go to your profile from the home screen and look through your "Learning History" to see any lessons that still need payment! </label>

          <label id="question">How do I review a lesson? </label>
          <label id="answer">Go to your profile from the home screen and look through your "Learning History" to review any past lessons! </label>

          <label id="question">How do I send a teacher a message? </label>
          <label id="answer">You can email them through our "Hiring Screen". To get there, go to "Looking to Teach", select an activity and a teacher and then click "Hire"! </label>

